an/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAKuBEMBz2ljpW3RNU-454h4kwauUSt3b9Q", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Trudy worked with Damian on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "November 9, 2019", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "Damian and I worked together at Intercontinental, Kuala Lumpur for nearly 2 years, in that duration as head of revenue, I found Damian extremely good at problem solving, with a can do attitude on revenue.  with a sound background in E/Commerce supported driving a strong revenue performance through our channels including digital platforms.\nDamian was a great team player and very good coach to his team, his leadership skills were sound.\nWould love to work with Damian again..", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Trudy Moreno", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "--", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/trudy-moreno-0924a6167/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACfC8u4BstULqba13iKy9jYCT5OYXmM3HS8", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Ahmad worked with Damian on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "April 26, 2018", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "I have worked very closely with Damian during my Area DOSM role with InterContinental Hotels Group based in Kuala Lumpur. Damian’s expertise in the various revenue, marketing and digital aspects of the travel trade had polished his experience in all these disciplines to spearhead IHG Malaysia commercial results. During the time we have worked together, we were able to activate a number of successful strategies which was facilitated by his team work,  commercial drive and sense of innovation. Damian is well respected within his team, thanks to his ability to communicate to all stakeholders at any level. Any organization would be blessed to have him as its talented leader.", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Ahmad Mehio", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "Seasoned Award Winning Hôtelière I Commercial success driver I Brand & Culture developer I Cluster operations initiator I Client & network relations evolver I Solution selling provider I Asset management enhancer", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/ahmad-mehio-0b220613/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAKzMQYBGjbqgOAZvG4HkyTh_LN_TQjrtp8", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Meera worked with Damian on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "April 26, 2018", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "Damian has a funny, easy-going personality which makes working together a pleasure. In the past 2 years that I have known him, he has changed roles a few times with multiple promotions. This is certainly testament to his hard work and self-development. \nI look forward to having the opportunity to work with Damian in future. ", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Meera Raj", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Head of SKS Hospitality | SKS Group", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/meera-raj/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAde4sYBonOJX8I1IQfRKwx0yO3ltfvHaro", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Peter managed Damian directly", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "June 30, 2016", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "I remember Damian's interview for this position - he brought along a detailed analysis of the hotel websites, OTA overview and social media presence.  The interview laid the foundation for the initial tasks in this role.  Damian was results focused in this role and used revenue growth as the ROI analysis for SEO/SEM campaigns he formulated.  Damian executed the hotel social media strategy, from replying to TripAdvisor reviews, driving upsell revenue from direct guest communications and setting the hotel as one of Kuala Lumpur's leading dining establishments in the local KL community.  Damian brought to the team a professionalism around online / digital revenue growth in a segment that was new to the hotel industry.  Damian partnered closely with reservations team and revenue management leaders to ensure that the hotel remained 'for sale' on the various distribution platforms.  Damian drove operational excellence and was a leader in this relatively new space for the hotel. ", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Peter Foreman", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "Sales, Marketing & Distribution - Singapore, Maldives at Marriott (Asia Pacific)", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/peteraforeman/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAKuBEMBz2ljpW3RNU-454h4kwauUSt3b9Q", "skills/0/title": "Next.js", "skills/1/title": "Linux", "skills/2/title": "PostgreSQL", "skills/3/title": "Cloudflare", "skills/4/title": "Team Leadership", "skills/5/title": "Market Planning", "skills/6/title": "Team Management", "skills/7/title": "Communication", "skills/8/title": "Restaurant Management", "skills/9/title": "Pricing Strategy", "skills/10/title": "Job Satisfaction", "skills/11/title": "Guest Satisfaction", "skills/12/title": "Financial Performance", "skills/13/title": "Customer Satisfaction (CSAT)", "skills/14/title": "Customer Satisfaction", "skills/15/title": "Business Strategy", "skills/16/title": "Digital Marketing", "skills/17/title": "Web Development", "skills/18/title": "Search Engine Ranking", "skills/19/title": "Social Media Marketing", "totalExperienceYears": "15.9", "totalRecommendationsGiven": "3", "totalRecommendationsReceived": "4", "urn": "ACoAAA7fZWUBy_tsOKhIBqhVdjRqIkJyosxgBSo"}$$::jsonb),
