r was housed on the restaurant wall for years and Guido looked after it flawlessly and with the upmost respect. Whenever l visited him at Carpaccio's, his hospitality was second to none and he was always extremely generous with his time and spirit. I would trust Guido with my life. He is one of a small handful of people l would like to call a friend for life.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Lara Katrina Compton", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "“In a world of power and privilege, one woman dared to obey her heart.” Leo Tolstoy, Anna Karenina My profile picture was taken by the wonderful David Emanuel!", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/lara-katrina-compton-422ba01/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABagFoBC-ST7f6MY5ADmF8fW-eWi62qSWU", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Bianca was Guido's client", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "March 16, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "Great food and service!", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Bianca Senna", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "CEO at Senna Brand US", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/bianca-senna-b92a485/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAELSJ4Bxz2b8HnAn-h6t2J1fXRbO68AVJM", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Guido was Angelo's client", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "January 15, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "Guido has been a customer of Vinum for a good number of years with different business, it has been a pleasure working with him and I hope in the near future to work with him again.", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Angelo Cane", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Managing Director, VinumTerra", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/angelo-cane-a5b01a5/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADkamcBkKBkrCg936dpe2cZ-PJjGClbZ8g", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Daniela worked with Guido